dct_title_s: Bird's eye view of the Holy Land
dct_description_sm: opyright by A.J. Marks ; Holy Land Pub. Co.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, settlements, places of historical interest.
Includes index: [Sites of historical and geological interest].
Appears in Cram's Illustrated family atlas of the world.
